item.title: Announcements
item.description: Todays blog post is less technical than the previous ones. I would like to talk about some events that happened in the last time. I am a registered Apple developer since November 2013. Since then I collected a lot of experiences, built a lot of apps and gained a ton of knowledge. But every product I built was for someone else, no matter if it was a company or a person.
